{"tid":2197390,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［德國戰線］習總，我們到了，你在哪裏","createTime":"2020-09-10T14:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T21:23:29.000Z","uid":230840,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"374f6d15b2430cb9583a3ff3e9fb5ce391bbe86a","tid":2197390,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"9月13號中国同歐盟本身會喺東德城市萊比錫( Leipzig)有經貿會議。呢個消息傳出咗冇幾耐，就有幾班德國手足密謀喺嗰幾日好好咁「迎接」嗰班首腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而輾轉之下，有一班萊比錫嘅local group發現大家志同道合，所以就一齊搞個盛大嘅「歡迎會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n本身都搞到七七八八，就係等嗰幾日。點知，一場武肺就打亂曬成個計劃，佢哋最後決定取消會談<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。雖然唔搞會談，但係歡迎會依舊，甚至搞得再大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係由Leipzig stands with Hong Kong、Germany stands with Hong Kong 、Wirf&uuml;rhk、Junge Taiwan Initiative 同No China EU summit一齊組織，喺9月11日至9月14日都有活動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNo EU China summit 就<br />\n係萊比錫當地本土青年組織，今次亦都係佢哋主動搵我哋手合作搞呢次活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDQRnby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDQRnby.jpg&h=2e8033bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLeipzig stands with Hong Kong Twitter:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Leipzigstandsw2?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLeipzigstandsw2%3Fs%3D09&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=46f0cb67\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Leipzigstandsw2?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\nGermany stands with Hong Kong Twitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/germany_with_hk?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgermany_with_hk%3Fs%3D09&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=dfdfe13d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/germany_with_hk?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\nWirf&uuml;rhk Twitter :<a href=\"https://twitter.com/w4hongkong?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fw4hongkong%3Fs%3D09&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=532018b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/w4hongkong?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\nJunge Taiwan Initiative Twitter:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JTIDCG?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJTIDCG%3Fs%3D09&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=a1f3a863\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JTIDCG?s=09</a><br />\n <br />\n No China EU summit Twitter:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/noeucn?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnoeucn%3Fs%3D09&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=5a9c0b0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/noeucn?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然我哋身處外地，但係我哋都係香港人。就算唔可以返香港都會用盡一切辦法去支援你哋，總有一日黎明會到，大家一定要留返條命見證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"> Freiheit f&uuml;r Hongkonger</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2af66b631a3fb0ba1e96e9be5955e3bc89944f3b","tid":2197390,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c13228193cea5b2e8f59d5533b52370cb642b66","tid":2197390,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb059e48ed6355f3417fa08bb10709bcb180a74","tid":2197390,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6f0a99afbe7a525a8097a11f004406a6489db21b","tid":2197390,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"43384a7f0e38fee7cc8bfbae726020eb7111cfe3","tid":2197390,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fb761bd0fb72fe1d16c50eae2326ffbc45ee62","tid":2197390,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">天滅中共，全黨死清光</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"462b7bfd480c8e1a4a8e12fc1c7a99f3caaaa29c","tid":2197390,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一息尚存，抗爭到底</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5482bef6129817f5783621543389e44f095ff1ca","tid":2197390,"uid":220519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3045115b2be229c4716192e819b45b2ddb4a23fa","tid":2197390,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14